introducing Mark Sweeney,

00:01:16.910 --> 00:01:20.290
the Associate Librarian of Library
Services who will welcome you

00:01:20.290 --> 00:01:22.310
to the Library of Congress.

00:01:22.310 --> 00:01:27.290
Mark Sweeney begin his career at
the Library of Congress in 1987

00:01:27.290 --> 00:01:30.130
in the Serial and Government
Publications Division.

00:01:30.130 --> 00:01:34.160
He then rose through the ranks
becoming unit supervisor,

00:01:34.160 --> 00:01:39.320
reference librarian, and reference
specialist, and eventually served

00:01:39.320 --> 00:01:42.160
as head of the newspaper section.

00:01:42.160 --> 00:01:46.440
