education and higher learning.

00:12:11.040 --> 00:12:16.990
We feel the critical task of any
society and government is to focus

00:12:16.990 --> 00:12:20.680
on and promote excellence
in education.

00:12:20.680 --> 00:12:22.400
Science and technology,

00:12:22.400 --> 00:12:26.120
and knowledge in general
are essential components

00:12:26.120 --> 00:12:28.970
of advancement and innovation.

00:12:28.970 --> 00:12:34.050
As a result of our education,
we grew up to believe that facts

00:12:34.050 --> 00:12:38.070
and knowledge rule supreme
and should be the key drivers

00:12:38.070 --> 00:12:41.390
of how we live and work in society.

00:12:41.390 --> 00:12:46.080
Within this context, the
value and status of educators

00:12:46.080 --> 00:12:48.790
and the educated is enormous.

00:12:48.790 --> 00:12:53.330
