challenges and disruptions.

00:13:18.810 --> 00:13:22.850
This culture is recognized for its
contribution to world literature

00:13:22.850 --> 00:13:27.940
and art, sciences, religion,
and advanced thinking.

00:13:27.940 --> 00:13:32.670 position:56%
