00:39:04.620 --> 00:39:09.760
But in fact, the longest continuous
wall in antiquity is this Wall

00:39:09.760 --> 00:39:12.170
of Gorgan, which was
meant to keep people --

00:39:12.170 --> 00:39:16.450
