6th Century who makes certain
adjustments to Zoroastrian law,

00:42:58.630 --> 00:43:02.480
which doesn't sit well with the
rest of the priestly I think group,

00:43:02.480 --> 00:43:07.910
and the king uses him for
to make certain changes

00:43:07.910 --> 00:43:10.850
and when Joseon comes
in eradicates him.

