And the story goes that
he invites Mazdak --

00:43:55.190 --> 00:43:57.970
he says, come and see
what you have planted.

00:43:57.970 --> 00:44:00.230
So again, this idea of
the king as the gardener.

00:44:00.230 --> 00:44:02.430
And you can see the
image from the Shahnameh

00:44:02.430 --> 00:44:06.450
