02:09:11.150 --> 02:09:18.680
for that beautifully crafted
discussion of interpretations

02:09:18.680 --> 02:09:21.290
and allegorical readings of texts,

02:09:21.290 --> 02:09:25.400
which again has very modern
echoes for all of us today.

02:09:25.400 --> 02:09:30.470
And the more we listen today, we
see how the borders we created

02:09:30.470 --> 02:09:36.950
between past and present are really
more imaginary than they exist.

02:09:36.950 --> 02:09:43.110
Also, thank you so much to Al
Borzean High School people here

02:09:43.110 --> 02:09:48.630
for brining -- can you imagine that
a high school established in Iran

02:09:48.630 --> 02:09:52.510
so long ago is bringing such
learned echoes to the Library

02:09:52.510 --> 02:09:54.700
of Congress and to all of us?

02:09:54.700 --> 02:09:56.000
That's wonderful.

02:09:56.000 --> 02:09:57.800
Thank you.

02:09:57.800 --> 02:10:02.090
