02:10:02.090 --> 02:10:06.850
Thank you, and our next
distinguished speaker,

02:10:06.850 --> 02:10:12.390
Professor Scott McDonough, is an
Associate Professor of History

02:10:12.390 --> 02:10:18.900
at William Patterson
University in New Jersey.

02:10:18.900 --> 02:10:23.360
His research interests lie
in the social, institutional,

02:10:23.360 --> 02:10:29.400
