02:10:44.690 --> 02:10:50.330
And the book is going
to appear in 2018.

02:10:50.330 --> 02:10:58.190
The title of Professor McDonough's
presentation today is "Queen Shirin

02:10:58.190 --> 02:11:03.220
and the Churches of the East,
Christianity in Sasanian Iran."

02:11:03.220 --> 02:11:05.460
Sounds to be very, very
interesting to listen to.

02:11:05.460 --> 02:11:09.510
Thank you, please welcome.

02:11:09.510 --> 02:11:16.060
