03:16:10.150 --> 03:16:16.550
In this presentation, I would
like to present some aspects

03:16:16.550 --> 03:16:21.060
of the cultural life, literary,
and mythical narrations that seem

03:16:21.060 --> 03:16:25.400
to have played an essential role
in the imperial construction

03:16:25.400 --> 03:16:28.590
of the Late Sasanian period.

03:16:28.590 --> 03:16:30.760
I think I don't need to stress,

03:16:30.760 --> 03:16:34.840
especially after the illuminating
