03:35:12.290 --> 03:35:17.840
of the Silk Road, specifically
that of the Sogdians

03:35:17.840 --> 03:35:22.750
and other Central Asians who
lived in China; and the artistic

03:35:22.750 --> 03:35:28.410
and political uses of Iran's
pre-Islamic visual past in the 19th

03:35:28.410 --> 03:35:29.790
and early 20th centuries.

