A Research Associate at
the Institute for the Study

03:35:34.560 --> 03:35:39.390
of the Ancient World, she is
a co-editor for the "Journal

03:35:39.390 --> 03:35:43.160 position:56%
of Inner Asian Art and Archaeology."

03:35:43.160 --> 03:35:49.070
She has a MA degree
from Columbia University

03:35:49.070 --> 03:35:52.320
and a PhD from Harvard University.

03:35:52.320 --> 03:35:53.620
Thank you very much.

03:35:53.620 --> 03:35:57.510
Let's have Dr. Lerner
