attracted Cook.

04:21:37.510 --> 04:21:41.560
Furthermore, Nilla Cook's
parents were among key figures,

04:21:41.560 --> 04:21:45.940
the key figures involved the
American [inaudible] Hellenist

04:21:45.940 --> 04:21:52.120
artistic movements in
1920s and the organizers

04:21:52.120 --> 04:21:56.630 position:56%
of the important Delphic Festival in
Greece for the revival of Persian --

04:21:56.630 --> 04:21:59.750
of pure ancient Greek traditions.

04:21:59.750 --> 04:22:05.450 position:56%
Growing up in Greece, Nilla not
only witnessed major American modern

04:22:05.450 --> 04:22:11.010 position:56%
