in search of natural dances in ruins

04:22:11.010 --> 04:22:16.490
of Athens but also was herself
involved in these dance activities.

04:22:16.490 --> 04:22:21.550
At the same time, like many
Orientalists of the wartime,

04:22:21.550 --> 04:22:24.440 position:56%
she worked with the U.S. government.

04:22:25.880 --> 04:22:31.680
Showing up in the wartime of Iran
in 1942, she temporarily was hired

04:22:31.680 --> 04:22:37.900 position:56%
by the American Embassy in Tehran as
a cultural relation representative.

04:22:37.900 --> 04:22:42.700
