of Theaters of Iranian Ministry

04:22:42.700 --> 04:22:46.960
of Interior as director
meaning that she was the --

04:22:46.960 --> 04:22:51.130
she was in charge of
censorship of theater and cinema

04:22:51.130 --> 04:22:56.910
which at the time was very
much influenced by the Soviets.

04:22:56.910 --> 04:23:01.860
Meanwhile, she pursued both Iranian
and American resources ranging

04:23:01.860 --> 04:23:05.170
from the embassy to
Shah's mother in order

04:23:05.170 --> 04:23:07.940 position:56%
to create an Iranian National Opera.

04:23:07.940 --> 04:23:14.590
Inferring from archival
research at my archival research

04:23:14.590 --> 04:23:17.810
